  "comment": "LCB300 LED BAR 36x3W RGBW: The LCB300 is a cutting-edge fixture that is packed with a lot of features to highlight any event or venue. With its 36x 3W RGBW LEDs, the LCB300 delivers powerful and versatile lighting performance. The LEDs are divided into 12 individually controllable sections, each comprising 3 LEDs. This level of control allows you to create mesmerizing light shows with stunning precision and flexibility. While using the fixture in stand-alone mode there are pre-programmed shows that you can run automatically or sound activated, pick from the pre-set colour macros or create your own mixture of colours in RGBW mode. The extra power output enables you to simply link the power of multiple units together into a single socket.\n\n",
